(1, '杠杆的原理', '杠杆的原理', '<p><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;vertical-align:baseline;&quot;; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-stretch: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box; font-stretch: inherit;\"><a style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box; font-stretch: inherit; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.bn016.com/\" target=\"_self\">股票配资</a>也叫股票融资。 很多投资者具有良好的盈利能力和风险控制能力，但受制于自身资金量较小，其盈利能力和资金管理的能力无法得到充分发挥。而解决这一问题最直接的方法就是扩大操作资金。股票配资是为具备丰富交易经验及风险控制能力的股票投资者提供的放大其操作资金的业务。很多人在做股票配资的都会碰到很问题，今天云沪深就为你介绍一下在做股票杠杆时会碰到的<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">二个常见问题</strong>。<br/></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;vertical-align:baseline;&quot;; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-stretch: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box; font-stretch: inherit;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">问题</strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">一、<a style=\"background: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box; font-stretch: inherit; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.bn016.com/\" target=\"_self\">股票配资</a>，是不是一定能赚钱 &nbsp;</strong></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;vertical-align:baseline;&quot;; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-stretch: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box; font-stretch: inherit;\">股票杠杆后就只是把你的本金扩大，获取的利益扩大，并没有说你配资后就一定会赚钱。当然要是你本身技术好，杠杆后收益扩大了，按照之前的比例算，那么你算赚钱了。但是这个前提是你有足够的把握在股市中能赚到钱。&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;vertical-align:baseline;&quot;; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-stretch: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; line-height: inherit; text-indent: 2em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#505050;vertical-align:baseline;&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box; font-stretch: inherit;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">问题</strong></span><strong style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-style: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit;\"></strong><strong style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-style: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit;\">二、配资的原理是金融杠杆。</strong></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;vertical-align:baseline;&quot;; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-stretch: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box; font-stretch: inherit;\">假设4倍杠杆，你出资1万，资方出资4万，你总共是5万操盘资金。盈亏用户自负。系统有警戒线和平仓线，当亏损到一定资金时，系统会提示您到底警戒线，再继续亏损则到达平仓线，这时系统会自动帮您卖出股票&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px currentcolor; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;vertical-align:baseline;&quot;; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; font-stretch: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\"><br/></p>', 'http://a.yunhushen.com/public/uploads/20200319/83162a55f8cfa560b774bb013342e02.png', 'http://a.yunhushen.com/public/uploads/20200319/wel18.png', 'http://a.yunhushen.com/public/uploads/20190627/83162a55f8cfa560b774bb013342e02.png', 1),
(2, '充值提现问题', '充值提现提盈常见问题', '<p>我们支持支付宝转账，银行卡转账充值！支付宝银行卡均是对公户！</p><p>交易时间内充值3分钟内到账！申请配资3分钟内通过！</p><p>工作日小额提现半小时内（一般是几分钟）到账，20万以上大额次日到账。</p><p>提盈条件是盈利3%以上可以提盈，总操盘资金的3%，提取超过3%的部分,提取100的整数倍。</p>', 'http://a.yunhushen.com/public/uploads/20200319/ce4fad341dd3fe50b63387d92af748d.png', 'http://a.yunhushen.com/public/uploads/20200319/wel19.png', 'http://a.yunhushen.com/public/uploads/20190627/ce4fad341dd3fe50b63387d92af748d.png', 1),
(3, '云沪深收费利率、仓位限制、交易手续费。', '云沪深收费利率，仓位限制', '<p>云沪深提醒您股市有风险，入市需谨慎；云沪深不存在任何荐股分成等指导性意见。云沪深是股票杠杆居间撮合服务商，撮合操盘方和投资方进行合作，投资人出资，操盘方支付保证金操盘。云沪深作为中介方，只进行居间撮合服务。</p><p>云沪深随时支持行情盘口挂单量变化测试，提供交割单，QQ远程查看券商母账户委托成交明细查看，均支持验证。<br/>分按日操盘、按月操盘，按日提供3-9倍操盘，按月操盘1-9倍操盘。</p><p>收益100%归您。</p><p>利息管理费详情看下图，买卖0.002手续费，卖出印花税0.001</p><p>充值资金申请账号五分钟内完成。</p><p>支持盘中提取盈利，当日卖出，当日提现，当日到账（20万以下当日，20万以上大额次日）</p><p>请关注每日公告中名单中被禁止买入的股票。</p><p>平仓线警戒线、持仓比例：</p><p><img src=\"http://a.yunhushen.com/public/uploads/20201111/1605107309503008.png\" title=\"1605107309503008.png\" alt=\"1605107309503008.png\" width=\"480\" height=\"225\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 480px; height: 225px;\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://a.yunhushen.com/public/uploads/20201111/1605107389878256.png\" title=\"1605107389878256.png\" alt=\"1605107389878256.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"200\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 410px; height: 200px;\"/></p><p>利率明细：</p><p><img src=\"http://a.yunhushen.com/public/uploads/20201111/1605103705414641.png\" title=\"1605103705414641.png\" alt=\"image.png\"/></p>', '', 'http://a.yunhushen.com/public/uploads/20190627/wel20.png', 'http://a.yunhushen.com/public/uploads/20190627/c4832664175f86de238671db88df414.png', 1),
(5, '联系我们', '客服热线：4001886760', '<p>电话热线：4001886760<br/>QQ在线：6272331<br/>微信公众号：云沪深</p>', 'http://a.yunhushen.com/public/uploads/20200319/17f0eb1fda5fa6641364dd773152623.png', 'http://a.yunhushen.com/public/uploads/20200319/wel22.png', 'http://a.yunhushen.com/public/uploads/20190627/17f0eb1fda5fa6641364dd773152623.png', 1),
(8, '免息体验规则', '免息体验有时间限制，超过时间，则禁止新创建持仓，且免息体验到期，自动平仓', '<p>免息体验3个交易日，只需要充值保证金，无需利息。免息体验到期，您需要在第3个交易日的14:50前卖出股票，未卖出系统自动平仓结算。</p>', 'http://a.yunhushen.com/public/uploads/20190610/火影4.jpg', '', NULL, 1);
